rows.label: qev041409_MSG0001
rows.name:
Welcome to Dopang Caravan. Not much to see here,
but friend should still relax and enjoy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041409_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Kupee about the caravan's business.

rows.label: qev041409_MSG0002
rows.name:
Unlike other Nopon, Kupee and others here not very
competitive.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041409_MSG0003
rows.name: Caravan sells just enough materials to keep going.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041409_MSG0004
rows.name:
Oh, and sometimes someone finds mysterious something
or other and everyone get excited. That can be fun![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041409_MSG0009
rows.name:
Hmm. Kupee understand. Kupee will draft contract for
friend to take back.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041409_MSG0010
rows.name:
When the time comes, caravan will send up great big
fireworks to cheer up Elder Nan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041409_MSG0012
rows.name: Friend should look forward to it![ST:wait ]
